abstract: United States military assists Somali forces in carrying out raid that kills several members of Shabab militant group in Saakow; it remains unclear whether any high-level operatives were killed.
lead_paragraph: It was not clear whether any high-level operatives had been eliminated in the assault, which took place last week.
